w" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wargasm-announce-new-single-bang-ya-head-featuring-limp-bizkits-fred-durst-3491740">Wargasm 宣布与 Limp Bizkit 的 Fred Durst 合作的新单曲“BANG YA HEAD”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
